# Rust
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
# `src-tauri/` is a workspace member, so the workspace root `Cargo.lock`
# is authoritative. The `src-tauri/Cargo.lock` is a vestigial artifact
# from before the workspace migration — never updated by cargo.
src-tauri/Cargo.lock

